 ('29', '77', '5', '1', 'en_us', '1', '', '{\"typeId\":null,\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Hudl Assist\",\"slug\":\"hudl-assist\",\"postDate\":1513453680,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"17\":\"Take a deeper look at the data you receive with Hudl Assist\\u2014plus tips and tricks to help uncover insights.\",\"19\":{\"new1\":{\"type\":\"block\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"Record like the pros.\",\"details\":\"<p>When you send games to Hudl Assist, we want to make sure you receive the best breakdowns. But our analysts can\\u2019t tag what they can\\u2019t see. That\\u2019s why it\\u2019s important to follow a few guidelines when it comes to recording your games. Record in HD, take shots of the scoreboard throughout the game\\u2013or just check out our full list of recording tips before your game.<\\/p>\",\"links\":\"<p><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.hudl.com\\/support\\/v3\\/breakdown-stats-and-reports\\/tag-games\\/tag-video-after-the-game\\\" class=\\\"sport\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noreferrer noopener\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/static.hudl.com\\/craft\\/icons\\/sport-svgs\\/basketball-dark-32.svg\\\" style=\\\"vertical-align:middle;height:auto;\\\" alt=\\\"basketball-dark-32.svg\\\"><\\/a>&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.hudl.com\\/support\\/v3\\/breakdown-stats-and-reports\\/hudl-assist\\/basketball-recommended-recording-workflow\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noreferrer noopener\\\">Basketball<\\/a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.hudl.com\\/support\\/v3\\/breakdown-stats-and-reports\\/tag-games\\/tag-video-after-the-match-soccer\\\" class=\\\"sport\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noreferrer noopener\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/static.hudl.com\\/craft\\/icons\\/sport-svgs\\/soccer-dark-32.svg\\\" style=\\\"vertical-align:middle;height:auto;\\\" alt=\\\"soccer-dark-32.svg\\\"><\\/a>&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.hudl.com\\/support\\/v3\\/breakdown-stats-and-reports\\/hudl-assist\\/soccer-recommended-recording-workflow\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noreferrer noopener\\\">Soccer<\\/a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.hudl.com\\/support\\/v3\\/breakdown-stats-and-reports\\/tag-games\\/tag-video-after-the-match-vb\\\" class=\\\"sport\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noreferrer noopener\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/static.hudl.com\\/craft\\/icons\\/sport-svgs\\/volleyball-dark-32.svg\\\" style=\\\"vertical-align:middle;height:auto;\\\" alt=\\\"volleyball-dark-32.svg\\\"><\\/a>&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.hudl.com\\/support\\/v3\\/breakdown-stats-and-reports\\/hudl-assist\\/volleyball-recommended-recording-workflow\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noreferrer noopener\\\">Volleyball<\\/a>&nbsp;<\\/p>\",\"helperImage\":[\"72\"],\"videoFile\":\"\"}},\"new2\":{\"type\":\"block\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"Submit your games to Hudl Assist.\",\"details\":\"<p>Once you\\u2019ve uploaded your game or received video from opponents, send it off to our analysts to be broken down.<\\/p>\\r\\n<ol><li>Select one or more videos in your library and click Send to Assist. If it\\u2019s an opponent scout video, select which team should be scouted as offense.<\\/li><li>Add jersey colors for each team.<\\/li><li>Leave a note for the analyst if there are missing clips or recording errors\\u2013any additional information that\\u2019ll help our analysts accurately break down the video.<\\/li><li>Once your breakdown is complete, you\\u2019ll receive an email from our analysts.<\\/li><\\/ol>\",\"links\":\"<p><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.hudl.com\\/support\\/v3\\/breakdown-stats-and-reports\\/hudl-assist\\/submit-a-game-to-hudl-assist\\\">Learn how to submit games to Assist.<\\/a><\\/p>\",\"helperImage\":[\"73\"],\"videoFile\":\"\"}},\"new3\":{\"type\":\"block\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"header\":\"Learn more about the data you receive.\",\"details\":\"<p>Curious what information you\\u2019ll receive from Hudl Assist? Take a deeper look at how o